  <title translate="true">SCARA</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">SCARA-Robot</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:459px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">SCARA</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is an acronym that stands for </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Selective Compliance Assembly Robot Arm</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-decoration:underline;" translate="true">Selective Compliance Articulated Robot Arm</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">It is a Robot that looks similar to the human arm. A servomotor between the Base and Upper-Arm at the Shoulder, a servomotor between the Upper-Arm and Fore-Arm at the Elbow, and a servomotor between the Fore-Arm and the Hand at the Wrist. There is a tool in the hand at the distal end.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
